## Footnotes

### Footnote Definitions

[^1]: This is a footnote with inline content.

[^long]: This footnote has a longer explanation that demonstrates
how footnotes work in Djot.

[^math]: Even math works in footnotes: $`x^2 + y^2 = z^2`

### Using Footnotes

Scientific claims need citations[^1].

Multiple footnotes[^long] can be used[^math] in the same paragraph.

